    "On the [img:Desktop version] Desktop version, [img:Console version] Console version, and [img:Mobile version] Mobile version, the Angler will not give you a Weather Radio as a reward if you already have one in your inventory or in any of your Portable Storages. However, if you have a Fisherman's Pocket Guide, Weather Radio, <b>and</b> Sextant (or at least one of the accessories crafted from them: the Fish Finder, PDA, or <span class=\"eil\"><span>Cell Phone</span><span class=\"eico s i1 i2 i4 i6\" title=\"Desktop, Console, Mobile and Legacy tModLoader versions\"><b></b><i></i></span></span>) in your inventories, he will be able to give you duplicate Weather Radios."
